css_rules.cssText: @font-face { font-family: "SF Pro Text"; src: url("/typeface/sf-pro-text-400.woff2") format("woff2"); font-weight: 400; }
@font-face { font-family: "SF Pro Text"; src: url("/typeface/sf-pro-text-500.woff2") format("woff2"); font-weight: 500; }
* { box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; }

html { font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.05px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "SF Pro Text", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif !important; }
body { padding: 40px 20px; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; scrollbar-gutter: stable both-edges; }
body > div { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; }
section { padding: 24px 0px; }
h1, h2, h3 { font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 400; }
h1 a { color: rgb(26, 26, 26); }
h3 { display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
a { text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.1s; }
b { font-weight: 500; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); }
h1 { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2px; }
h3 { font-weight: 500; }
h4 { color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-weight: 400; }
.header { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.header > b:first-of-type { margin-bottom: 2px; }
.bio { display: block; padding: 1px 0px; }
.bio a { display: inline-block; }
.markdown { line-height: 1.5; }

.link, .markdown a { position: relative; display: inline-flex; gap: 4px; padding: 4px 0px; margin: -2px 0px; transition: color 50ms cubic-bezier(0.55, 0.055, 0.675, 0.19), background-color 50ms, margin 50ms, box-shadow 50ms, padding 50ms; color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-weight: 500; }

.link::after, .markdown a::after { content: ""; position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; bottom: 4px; height: 1px; background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); transition: background-color 0.2s ease-out, bottom 0.2s ease-out, transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.785, 0.135, 0.15, 0.86), height 0.1s ease-out; }

.link::before, .markdown a::before { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 10px 0px 6px; background-color: rgba(0, 128, 255, 0); transition: border-radius 0.1s, background-color 50ms cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1), left 50ms, right 50ms, top 50ms, bottom 50ms; border-radius: 0.5px; }
.link:hover, .markdown a:hover { color: rgb(0, 128, 255); }
.link:hover::after, .markdown a:hover::after { background-color: rgba(0, 128, 255, 0.16); bottom: 4px; height: 1.5px; }
.link:hover::before, .markdown a:hover::before { inset: 6px -2px 5px; border-radius: 2px; background-color: rgba(0, 128, 255, 0.02); }
.ext { font-size: 12px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.reg { font-weight: 400; }
.co::after { opacity: 0; }
.co:hover::after { opacity: 1; }
.co:hover b { color: rgb(0, 128, 255); }
.founder a, .founder b, .founder span { font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; }
.title { display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.writing { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: repeat(4, 72px); padding: 20px 0px; gap: 28px; }
.article { display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: flex-start; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); }

.book { position: relative; justify-content: flex-start; min-height: 58px; max-height: 58px; min-width: 48px; max-width: 48px; margin-right: 16px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32) 0px 4px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 1px 2px 1px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 2px -1px; transition: box-shadow 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1); }
.book, .clip { display: flex; align-items: center; border-radius: 2px; }

.clip { position: absolute; inset: 0px -2px 0px 0px; z-index: 3; overflow: hidden; opacity: 1; justify-content: center; transform: translateX(-2px); mix-blend-mode: darken; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }

.shadow { left: 0px; max-width: 35.5px; min-width: 35.5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); z-index: 1; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32) 2px 0px 2px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 1px 0px 1px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 2px 0px 1px -2px; transition: opacity 0.5s, transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94); }
.drop-shadow, .shadow { position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; opacity: 0; transform: translateX(4px); }

.drop-shadow { min-width: 14.5px; right: 0px; z-index: 2; border-top-right-radius: 2px; border-bottom-right-radius: 2px; filter: saturate(2); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1), transform 0.2s; }

.chevron-right { color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: absolute; z-index: 10; right: 1.5px; opacity: 0; filter: drop-shadow(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75) 0px 0px 0px); transform: translateX(-1px); transition: opacity 0.2s, filter 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
.article:hover .book { box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6) 0px 4px 4px -2px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 4px 2px -2px; }
.article:hover .shadow { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0px); }
.article:hover .drop-shadow { opacity: 0.75; transform: translateX(0px); }
.article:hover .chevron-right { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0px); }
.cover { position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; inset: 0px; border-radius: 2px; z-index: 3; }
.post { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; margin-top: -4px; }
.post p { font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); }
button { outline: none; border: none; }

.btn { position: relative; z-index: 2; display: flex; max-height: 28px; min-height: 28px; min-width: 28px; padding: 6px; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; gap: 4px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: radial-gradient(circle closest-corner at 50% 66%, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01)); box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.04) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.2) 0px 1px 2px 1px, rgba(207, 207, 207, 0.2) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.06) 0px 2px 1px 0px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.2) 0px 2px 4px -2px; transform: translate(0px); transition: background-position 0.4s, color 0.4s, transform 0.12s ease-out, box-shadow 0.12s ease-in-out; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: "SF Pro Text", system-ui; font-weight: 500; user-select: none; }

.btn:hover { background-image: radial-gradient(circle farthest-side at 50% 72%, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.12), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01)); box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01) 0px 0px 0px 0px inset, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.06) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.4) 0px 1px 2px 1px, rgba(207, 207, 207, 0.2) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08) 0px 3px 1px 0px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.32) 0px 2px 4px -2px; transform: translateY(-0.5px); color: rgb(26, 26, 26); }

.btn:active { box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0px 0px 0px 20px inset, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.12) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.04) 0px 2px 2px 1px, rgba(207, 207, 207, 0.2) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.01) 0px 3px 1px 0px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.02) 0px 2px 4px -2px; transform: translateY(0.5px); }

.btn:focus { box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.02) 0px 1px 0px 6px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.04) 0px 1px 2px 1px, rgba(207, 207, 207, 0.2) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.02) 0px 2px 1px 0px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.04) 0px 2px 4px -2px; }
.btn.btn-e { position: static; margin-right: 2px; background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08); font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; font-weight: 500; }
.btn.btn-close, .btn.btn-e { max-width: none; background-image: none; box-shadow: none; }

.btn.btn-close { max-height: 20px; min-height: 20px; min-width: 20px; padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 6px; column-gap: 4px; border-radius: 6px; background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.04); transition: background-color 0.2s, background-position 0.4s, color 0.4s, transform 0.12s ease-out, box-shadow 0.12s ease-in-out; }
.btn.btn-close:active { background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08); }

.btn.tertiary { padding: 6px 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: none; box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.12) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 0px 1px 2px 1px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 0px 2px 1px 0px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0px 2px 4px -2px; }

.btn.tertiary:hover { box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.16) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 0px 1px 2px 1px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 0px 2px 1px 0px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0px 2px 4px -2px; transform: translate(0px); }
.btn.tertiary:active { transform: translateY(0.5px); }

.btn.tertiary:focus { box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.16) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) 0px 0px 0px 4px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 0px 2px 1px 0px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0px 2px 4px -2px; }
.map-container { position: relative; min-height: 360px; max-height: 360px; width: 100%; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); }
.map-container::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: -16px; left: 0px; right: 0px; border-top: 0.5px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); }

.map-controls { position: absolute; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; right: 0px; padding: 6px 8px; border-bottom-left-radius: 7px; border-bottom-right-radius: 7px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; z-index: 10; border-top: 0.5px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); }
.map-controls span { font-size: 14px; }
.eZCmWD { position: relative; min-width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0px auto; }

.HBHpS { margin-top: -2px; border-radius: 100%; width: 50px; height: 50px; border: 3px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; position: relative; left: -1.5px; }
.tjXPq { position: absolute; width: calc(100% - 6px); height: calc(100% - 6px); border-radius: 100%; z-index: 10; }
.heMkhj { width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 16px; }
.gTjuma { display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.jDUgMf { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.jDUgMf b:first-of-type { margin-bottom: 2px; }
.fJMlpX { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: repeat(4, 72px); margin-top: -8px; padding: 20px 0px; gap: 28px; }

.fapTP { margin-top: 4px; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 1px 0px 0px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 0px 2px 4px -2px; transform: translateY(0px); transition: transform 400ms cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1), box-shadow 200ms, filter 200ms; }

.fapTP:hover { box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 1px 0px 0px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 3px 5px -2px; transform: translateY(-1px); filter: brightness(97.5%); }
.hNKEFD { display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 8px; box-shadow: rgb(221, 221, 221) 0px -0.5px 0px 0px; padding-top: 16px; }
.jsVXfw { display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; gap: 10px; margin-right: auto; }

.bIfqyW { position: absolute; inset: 0px; z-index: 1; border-radius: 100%; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgb(245, 245, 245), rgb(242, 242, 242) 40%, rgb(255, 255, 255) 72%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01) 90%), linear-gradient(rgba(252, 252, 252, 0.2) 84%, rgb(10, 10, 10) 92%); box-shadow: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.02) 0px 1px 12px 16px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.36) 0px 6px 4px -1px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.04) 0px 1px 2px 1px, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.12) 0px 2px 2px -1px; }
.hTZjiR { width: 100%; height: 130px; background: white; border: none; margin-top: 8px; }
.fcOuxG { font-size: 14px; height: 28px; }
.gfmmRq { position: relative; bottom: 0.5px; }

.emJHJB { width: 100%; height: 100%; position: absolute; inset: 0px; border-radius: 2.5px; z-index: 1; background: transparent; box-shadow: transparent 0px 2px 0px 0px; filter: saturate(1.4) brightness(1.2); }
